OL,3,CCamping stove triggers large heath fire
OL,5,FFirefighters say a heath fire was
OL,6,Faccidentally started by camping stove
OL,7,Fwhich set alight a tent.
OL,9,FThe fire then spread across a large
OL,10,Farea on Soldiers Road, Norden in
OL,11,FDorset.
OL,13,FCrews from Wareham, Poole, Swanage,
OL,14,FRedhill Park, Westbourne and
OL,15,FSpringbourne, were called to deal with
OL,16,Fthe blaze on Friday 17 July at 7.41pm.
OL,18,FIt took them almost four hours to
OL,19,Fbeing the fire under control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
