OL,3,CCamping stove triggers large heath fire
OL,5,FA spokesperson from Wareham Fire
OL,6,FStation said: "Please don't light open
OL,7,Ffires or use disposable barbecues.
OL,9,F"Instead, pack a picnic and help
OL,10,Fprotect our countryside for everyone
OL,11,Fto enjoy.
OL,13,F"A simple choice can prevent a major
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,F"Thank you for doing your part."
OL,18,FThe fire affected approximately 100m x
OL,19,F40m of heath.
